Requirements:
1. Support multiple elevators
2. outside box -> up down request
3. inside elevator -> destination
4. should show current status -> floor where it is, door status-> open closed
5. Other features -> emergency stop, overload detection, maintenance mode, alert bell

Entities:
1. ElevatorManagement System
2. Elevator ->
3. Buttons -> floor buttons, special ones -> (emergency stop, overload detection, maintenance mode, alert bell)
4. Floor -> Direction buttons
5. Button Factory
6. Display

ElevatorManagementSystem
    List<Elevator> elevators;
    List<Floor> floors;

Elevator -> floorNo: number
            door status: open/close
            display
            List<Buttons> /map of buttons

Floor ->  boolean upRequest
          boolean downRequest



